From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Tue, 17 Mar 2026 08:10:31 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Fix SEO: dynamic robots, security headers, metadata gaps,
 structured data

- next.config.ts: Add compression, image optimization (avif/webp), security
  headers (X-Content-Type-Options, X-Frame-Options, Referrer-Policy), and
  static asset cache-control
- robots.ts: Dynamically compute sitemap count from building total instead
  of hardcoding 15; remove /review/new from disallow list
- layout.tsx: Add font-display: swap to Geist fonts to prevent CLS
- seo.ts: Add aggregateRating to landlordJsonLd; add newsArticleJsonLd helper
- landlord page: Pass avgScore to landlordJsonLd for rich snippet eligibility
- compare page: Add canonical URL and full OpenGraph metadata
- search page: Add revalidate=60, description, canonical, OpenGraph metadata
- unit page: Add canonical URL and OpenGraph metadata
- rankings page: Fix canonical URL to use city-prefixed path

https://claude.ai/code/session_01U5mQW2v8xyLTVMXHJQWaj1
